{"tid":2259803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報復台灣驅逐李彬豪 學生動源前召集人鍾翰林被國安處拘捕","createTime":"2020-10-27T05:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T07:14:05.000Z","uid":337052,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"67a2cd35bd9d4232bc88c369b5bd2ca10ff6c590","tid":2259803,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">港媒：學生動源前召集人鍾翰林被國安處拘捕</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/10/27 13:02<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者張謙香港27日電）<span class=\"red\">主張「香港獨立」的團體「學生動源」今早在臉書發文，指前召集人鍾翰林今早失聯，有報導表示，鍾翰林再次被警方國家安全處人員逮捕。</span><br />\n<br />\n學生動源在臉書放發的英文訊息指出，鍾翰林自今早8時之後失聯，不在家裡，無法找到其行蹤，而鍾翰林因為涉嫌違反港區國安法，預定今天到警署報到。<br />\n<br />\n香港「01」網就此刊登報導指出，鍾翰林已被國安處人員拘捕，暫未知原因。<br />\n<br />\n鍾翰林曾於7月29日遭國安處人員拘捕，指他涉嫌煽動他人分裂國家，其後獲准交保外出。<br />\n<br />\n在港區國安法於7月1日凌晨實施前，<span class=\"red\">學生動源公布，召集人鍾翰林已根據組織會章停止香港一切事務，即日起遣散香港全體成員</span>，組織事務將交由海外成員繼續運作，學生動源海外成員將設立外國分部接管組織一切事務。（編輯：翟思嘉）1091027<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202010270112.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202010270112.aspx&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=d3567b52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202010270112.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"2a4be0a599a597ab586e023cac0f87514d2b4c9a","tid":2259803,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/X41VLi18UeMd42_lxaj8sXpJIKs=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5WOCKRAIMFFGXBMD2KNR5DHBMM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FX41VLi18UeMd42_lxaj8sXpJIKs%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5WOCKRAIMFFGXBMD2KNR5DHBMM.jpg&h=d0129026&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65a8be837073206ebe8d458429c1b3d3f65f8827","tid":2259803,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:00:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94651505bec424f4d10a5711c2147a8d36e62e35","tid":2259803,"uid":54549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b9fbe7db8c8ef40f7df3350728cd8affe1c155","tid":2259803,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:04:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">李彬豪遭台驅逐 違法助港黨媒跟蹤鍾翰林「行為不容於民主法治社會」</span></strong><br />\n更新時間 (HKT): 2020.10.25 20:32<br />\n<br />\n（新增內容）<span class=\"red\">前「學生動源」召集人鍾翰林、洪英棠與洪心弦去年1月赴台灣，與《自由時報》政治組副主任蘇永耀、台灣青年反共救國團理事長楊月清見面，卻被偷拍放上香港《文匯報》、《大公報》頭版稱兩人暗會總統蔡英文「密使」。</span>台灣移民署今（25日）表示，<span class=\"red\">香港人李彬豪在台灣不法從事跟蹤拍攝港青訪問活動，其行為已違反《港澳條例》等規定，故廢止其在台居留許可，並於今日強制驅逐出境，且管制一定期間不得赴台。</span><br />\n<br />\n陸委會今日表示，除依照《港澳居民入台許可辦法》規定廢除李彬豪居留許可外，李已遭任職的科技公司解僱，原在台的居留身份亦已遭移除。陸委會又指，案件經台北地檢署調查，李彬豪在台從事與居留目的不符的情報蒐集工作，移民署依法查處案件，並於今天執行強制出境，並強調：「政府絕不容忍此類涉及侵害人身安全及隱私的不當行為，一旦發生，必定會追究相關責任，依法嚴懲到底。」<br />\n<br />\n今早7時許，李彬豪被帶往機場，乘搭長榮航空BR851早上8時05分班機返回香港，原定10時05分抵達，而航班提早於早上9時41分抵達香港國際機場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/k5qI7AQXHJXAPssmRlSXZrhtYmg=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J7LQPWFCCNEURAFD6UA6THUAOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fk5qI7AQXHJXAPssmRlSXZrhtYmg%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ7LQPWFCCNEURAFD6UA6THUAOA.jpg&h=4c8dc4c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李彬豪今日被押送到桃園機場，準備遣返回港。<br />\n(蘋果新聞網)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">鍾翰林：阻嚇性似乎太低</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n對於李彬豪被台灣驅逐出境，前「學生動源」召集人鍾翰林對《蘋果》表示，驅逐出境的阻嚇性似乎有點低，只是將他送回香港，是否有效阻止同類事件發生成疑，不論是針對在台灣的香港人，或者是台灣的本地人，鍾翰林認為，最理想是他可以在台灣負上一定刑責。<br />\n<br />\n鍾翰林又稱，在台灣被跟蹤之前，從2016年起他都已經間歇性被人跟蹤，他都無法確定跟蹤者的身份，過去他想，即使是被跟蹤，只要不影響他的生活，他都以平常心面對，「在台灣、在其他地方、在香港都好，他們要去做這件事（跟蹤）都會很容易」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣偵探社「一統徵信」被控受李彬豪委託，跟蹤香港學運人士鍾翰林等人赴台行程，照片輾轉交由《大公報》等港媒刊登。李彬豪受查時表示，是受到香港一間偵探社Pi Investigation委託，才找上「一統徵信」。台北地檢署認為徵信業者行為可鄙，但內容非屬非公開活動，不構成妨害秘密，不起訴。<br />\n<br />\n對此，移民署今日發出新聞稿表示，港人李彬豪違反居留目的，在台不法從事跟監拍攝港青參訪活動，其行為已違反港澳條例等規定，予以廢止居留許可，今天將他強制驅逐出境，並管制一定期間不得來台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6aRM_dPIhJEq41OpS74yytxehRA=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SFWF2QKU3VASJP2PWG6VOQBXSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6aRM_dPIhJEq41OpS74yytxehRA%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSFWF2QKU3VASJP2PWG6VOQBXSQ.jpg&h=ce4e4004&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前學生動源召集人鍾翰林去年赴台灣全程被人跟蹤偷拍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">移民署：外來人士應遵守法律</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n內政部長徐國勇表示，台灣是自由民主的國家，不論國人及外來人士在台均有免於恐懼的自由，部份紅色媒體以僱用偵探社跟蹤拍攝等不法手段在台蒐集情報，明顯利用台灣的自由民主進行滲透、傷害人權，其行為不為民主法治社會所認同。<br />\n<br />\n移民署強調，外來人士在台應遵守中華民國法律，如有不法情事，治安機關將依法究處。台灣當局還點名《大公報》、《文匯報》過去早有「前科」，在今次案件水落石出前，3年內不准兩間媒體赴台採訪。<br />\n<br />\n香港《蘋果》記者據履歷網頁「cake resume」資料，發現李彬豪是香港大學專業進修學院的副學士，2015年赴台就讀輔大心理系，去年畢業後曾在科技公司擔任業務工程師。然而，事件被揭發後，其資料現已遭移除了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201025/Z2LCO37APZFSZHGK25TEMFRBD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201025%2FZ2LCO37APZFSZHGK25TEMFRBD4%2F&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=287c8174\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201025%2FZ2LCO37APZFSZHGK25TEMFRBD4%2F&h=cdfcdb7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201025/Z2LCO37APZFSZHGK25TEMFRBD4/</a>"},{"pid":"2413755d9e7c941bf6d951e058293444ed456f4a","tid":2259803,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f274d54b15093995fe77cb9c60a4ae0b535e0941","tid":2259803,"uid":25424,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:06:48.000Z","msg":"即係俾人掟返香港條友堅有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf98f81a1e897ca6097df5736dab2333b909021","tid":2259803,"uid":114781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:08:52.000Z","msg":"支那狗又玩報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e1127e6169e257553bc37b59c0d05e81b1d439","tid":2259803,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TvXOqjw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTvXOqjw.jpg&h=789cefc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBrian Lee 李彬豪"},{"pid":"20f0c26f760fcafc3e67f90d13c44c8528e3377c","tid":2259803,"uid":185656,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a3e1127e6169e257553bc37b59c0d05e81b1d439","tid":2259803,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TvXOqjw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTvXOqjw.jpg&h=789cefc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBrian Lee 李彬豪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:10:23.000Z","msg":"獐頭鼠目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d682e13e7410c0fd46dd402f9b984bf6f0777128","tid":2259803,"uid":34410,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a3e1127e6169e257553bc37b59c0d05e81b1d439","tid":2259803,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TvXOqjw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail